title: Maitreya Healthy Vegetarian Resturant
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Chinese, Taiwanese, Cambodian, Khmer
description: Moved and re-opened here Feb 2016, near Tuol Tom Pong (replaced former Miao Xiang Xi eatery). Vegetarian restaurant with an extensive menu, uses mock meats in addition to veggies. No English. Note: Please send exact map coordinates to happycow!
